  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b85\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc7\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0baf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1 54 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "54 people arrested with boat trying to sail to Australia illegally",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lankan navy has seized a boat carrying 54 people illegally to Australia off the east coast.",
        "54 persons have been arrested in the Batticaloa-Palameenmadu waters for attempting to enter Australia illegally.",
        "A total of 54 people were arrested this morning following a naval siege.",
        "The Navy said that steps have been taken to bring the detainees to the Trincomalee port.",
        "The economic crisis in the country has led to an increase in the number of illegal immigrants to countries such as India and Australia in recent times."
      ],
